.Dd $Mdocdate: July 4 2017 $
.Dt OO-PUNCT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Oo-punct
.Nd punctuation handling by the Oo macro
.Sh DESCRIPTION
at the beginning:
.Oo "(" z
.Oo | z
.Oo . z
.Oc Oc "Sy" bold Oc
.Pp
in the middle:
.Oo a "(" z
.Oo a | z
.Oo a . z
.Oc Oc Oc
.Pp
at the end:
.Oo Oo a (
.Oc |
.Oc
.Pp
missing blank:
.Oo a.
.Oc
